Restlet Extensions 2.3.12 - Google Web Toolkit

Restlet Extensions extend the Restlet API and the Restlet Engine.

See: Description

Standards support 
Package Description
org.restlet.client.ext.json
Support for JSON representations.
org.restlet.client.ext.xml
Support for XML and XSLT representations.
Restlet Extensions extend the Restlet API and the Restlet Engine. This documentation corresponds to the Google Web Toolkit edition.

The Restlet Framework is led by Restlet, Inc. with the help of the Restlet community.
